                "default": [
                    "Salt wind rolls in from the Sea of Swords, carrying gull cries and a clean bite of spray.",
                    "Low cloud presses over the harbor while damp breezes turn streets and rigging slick.",
                    "The sky breaks bright over the coast, with brisk air and long silver light on the water.",
                ],
            },
            "forest": {
                "default": [
                    "Cool shade gathers beneath the trees, and the air smells of wet bark and leaf mold.",
                    "A soft rain ticks through the canopy, muting distant sounds and deepening every trail rut.",
                    "Sun shafts move between high branches while the undergrowth steams after earlier rain.",
                ],
            },
            "mountain": {
                "default": [
                    "Thin wind scrapes across the heights, sharp enough to make every exposed ledge feel higher.",
                    "Clouds snag on the peaks and spill cold mist through passes and mine roads.",
                    "Clear mountain light reveals far ridgelines, but the air turns bitter as soon as shadows lengthen.",
                ],
            },
            "plains": {
                "default": [
                    "Open wind combs the grasslands, bending trail dust into pale ribbons.",
                    "A wide, fair sky hangs over the road with only distant cloudbanks to mark the horizon.",
                    "Fast-moving showers sweep across the plain, brief enough to pass but heavy enough to soak packs.",
                ],
            },
            "swamp": {
                "default": [
                    "Humid air lies heavy over black water, and pale mist clings to reeds and drowned roots.",
                    "Warm rain patters on standing pools while insects rise in whining clouds.",
                    "A stale breeze pushes marsh fog across the path and hides the shape of the next hummock.",
                ],
            },
            "desert": {
                "default": [
                    "Dry heat shimmers over the flats, and every distant ridge looks closer than it is.",
                    "A gritty wind worries at cloaks and packs, carrying the smell of dust and old stone.",
                    "The day is clear and punishing, with cold waiting behind the first long shadow.",
                ],
            },
            "tundra": {
                "default": [
                    "Cold air cuts over hard ground, and low cloud promises snow before nightfall.",
                    "A pale sun hangs above the ice, bright but almost warmthless.",
                    "Wind-driven flurries blur tracks within minutes and turn every landmark uncertain.",
                ],
            },
            "ocean": {
                "default": [
                    "Long swells lift the horizon while steady wind fills sails and snaps loose lines.",
